dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until processing started (days)",
    "Time until notification completed (days)",
    "Notifications completed late (%)",
    "Notifications completed but open (%)",
    "Notifications without processing (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Service notifications processing started") 
        	AS "Time until processing started (days)",
		AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Processed service notifications completed") 
        	AS "Time until notification completed (days)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Service notifications completed after required end date") * 100 
        	AS "Notifications completed late (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Service notifications completed but order still open") * 100 
        	AS "Notifications completed but open (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Completed service notifications without processing") * 100 
        	AS "Notifications without processing (%)"
	
    FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
